'''Sudan''' ko [[leydi]] e [[Afirik]]. Leysdi Sudan ɗi go’o eder lesde yeɓere woila eta funa Afirika edi e kerol e lesde jewenayi. E ta woila lesdi Misra e ta funa [[Eritereya|Eriterea]] e [[Ethiopia]] e ta funa [[Kenya]] e [[Ugannda|Uganda]] e ta fombina woje funa [[Konngo (Ndenndaandi Demokaraasiyankeeri Konngo)|Congo]] den taugal [[Afirik|Afirika]] gondun Shaka (Central Afirika) e ta hirna [[Caadi|Chadi]] ɗen e ta woila woje hirna [[Libiya|Libya]] kamma un leysdi tokkuɗi dina juldaku.<ref>https://www.britannica.com/place/Sudan</ref>
