== Lasdi/Bolle Leysdi ==
Sudan e wodi ɗemle koɓuri taimere joyi kamma ɗemgal Larabankore ɗuɗi yimbe wolwoɓeɗe e mare gaɗa Larabankore Hausa 99,999,999 Haire ke wolde tataure (3) mare ɗun ɗe e fu yajuki lesdi nuba kamma haire ke nagaure 

== Haaire ke Wolde ==
Tatour inare ɗunɗe  e fu yajuki lesdi nuba kamma haire ke nagaure ɗen luttuɗe ɗen kauti e [[Mahras]], [[Damagla]], [[Zaghawa]], [[Tirgrinya]], [[Fulfulde]], [[Burgo]], [[Tama]], [[Masalit]], [[Nuwair]], [[Shuluk]] e luttuɗe (etc).

== Inaje Yilaru Omtukigite ==

* Wuro goɗun roti huɗe ɗenno lesdi ɗin kartum galliwol darfour kaje jabal mara inare ɓurɗe huɗe ɗenno e sudan.
* Kaje Darfour
* Galliwol kasala ɗuɗirka maɓɓe ɗun hausa en jodi wuro daruki kusel ladde e gelle Dindir.

== Inaje Leysdi Ɗin ==

* Sudan e wodi/mari inaje sappoje ɗiɗi e jewe go’o hanje goni:
* Leddi woilari Darfur
* Fombinari Darfur
* Woilajun Darfur
* Hirnajun Bahar Elgazal
* Elestuwaiya Shakajun
* Elestuwaiya Hirnajun
* Elustuwaiya Funajun
* Arɗibe Sudan gaɗa hebtuge hore mari.

